name: WATCH OUT
description:
This piece was from the time we were recording a song and I decided to snap photos of my friends and I made this. It was an amazing experience to be able to collaborate with people with such creative talents.
Our recorded song 'LAYA' featuring RIGHTEOUS ONE, HAKOB (Jakestudyos), Lawrence Jimenez, and ZENDO all from Titik Poetry will be airdropped to those who will be collecting this piece!

two birds in one stone!!!
